Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:08.21,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:13.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:16.71,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,今天也是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:19.41,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:22.54,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,波奇 今天有什么安排吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:25.32,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,在中午之前请您自便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.40,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,午餐将与毒太郎一同进餐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:30.31,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,毒太郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:32.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:34.13,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,没有其他人要来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.35,0:00:35.04,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.61,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,这里没人会来 请别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:39.25,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:40.93,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.15,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我得八点半去上学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.32,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.12,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,那么请先更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:50.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我做作业了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:51.34,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,您做了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:52.75,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.25,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,谢谢你 波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:54.92,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:59.45,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:00.38,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,您请
