Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.44,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哦 叶香公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:02.46,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您的脸色更胜往日 既帅气又性感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.32,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.51,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您竟会和我这样低贱之人打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:08.77,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,鄙人波伊森·毒太郎 喜不自胜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:11.81,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是说 感到极致光荣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.81,0:03:13.93,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,午饭 吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:18.42,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,十倍辣咖喱和吾野产醋拌苦瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:20.29,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:21.77,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这样的乡下料理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.92,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可能不合叶香公主的口味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.92,0:03:26.39,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是说 赶快去重做！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:27.37,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我能吃苦瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.91,0:03:30.48,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是 为什么要吃苦瓜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.44,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,在保谷采购的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.95,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,似乎是商队带过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.02,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.14,0:03:41.27,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,吾野…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.58,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啊呀呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.58,0:03:45.27,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,波奇君 一直以来辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:47.81,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,「波奇君」和不肖「毒太郎」都是「Po」开头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:51.67,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,同为Po人 让我们一起对公主献上忠诚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:52.79,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我正为此而效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:57.73,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真是的 波奇奇你一直在考虑着公主的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.03,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真可爱！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.17,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,你也要吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.37,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.42,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,当然当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:05.55,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.84,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.57,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,昆太郎先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.57,0:04:12.17,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是毒太郎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.41,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,豚太郎先生 你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:15.02,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:17.24,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你不是经常来玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.67,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我只是在想为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.68,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真是的 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.79,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主您这玩笑开大了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.04,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,怎么忘记了您的头号忠臣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:27.29,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我是市长波伊森毒太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.76,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,还请您务必记下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.06,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,虽然你说着公主 忠臣什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.30,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但我不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.78,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不如说 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.02,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,{\an8}您这说的什么话！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.02,0:04:36.01,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您忘记了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.31,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,公主您莅临池袋的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:41.09,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是说 池袋迎接公主您来的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.09,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,来池袋的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.05,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,欢迎公主您的不是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.61,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,正是鄙人毒太郎啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:48.49,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,您不记得了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.49,0:04:49.90,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这是何等的悲伤！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:53.28,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果您允许我用更多术语描述的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.28,0:04:55.38,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,果然还是很伤心 就是这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.49,0:05:02.54,Default,Man 1,0,0,0,,是那个女孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:03.67,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.67,0:05:05.27,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是她成为了触发器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:07.57,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,从随身物品看 她应该叫中富叶香
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.36,0:05:11.41,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\bord0.601\pos(791.665,158.67)}{\fs98.001}第{\fs103.001}9{\fs}{\fs98.001}话    可能比我想象中无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:09.77,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,吾野来的高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.77,0:05:11.29,Default,Man 2,0,0,0,,早知道会变成现在这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:13.27,Default,Man 2,0,0,0,,还不如听从那些家伙的忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:13.89,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:16.23,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,对外就说一切都在意料之内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:19.42,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,事到如今才说7G失败了 怎么开得了口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.96,Default,Man 1,0,0,0,,把这一切复原的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.14,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,喂喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.82,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,谁敢担这个责啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.64,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,装聋作哑维持现状就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:26.93,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,又没旁人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:28.84,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,倒是有人知道 但是他脑子寄了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.86,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,只要处理好这个女人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:31.38,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.38,0:05:33.06,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,绝对别让她离开视线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.13,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.91,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,稍微有点纰漏的话 就别想吃饭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:39.09,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.47,0:05:40.71,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:42.14,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.68,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我之前在做什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.94,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,感觉一切都很模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:51.11,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是时候起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.98,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:55.02,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,必须得散步才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.33,0:05:58.21,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我被告知大便也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.39,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,请快点起床
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.09,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我们去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:06.98,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你就像波奇一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:07.91,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,「波奇」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:10.82,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,喜欢散步 总是和我在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.68,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我家养的大狗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.84,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,而且既强大又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.02,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:19.16,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,那么 请叫我波奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:21.18,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我会永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:23.45,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我的身体变得很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.13,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,多半 还很强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:29.64,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,虽然现在很难飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:32.01,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,但这不是什么大问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.01,0:06:33.27,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但是 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.80,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我是波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:36.46,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我们去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:39.99,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这里就是池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:41.54,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,看着是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.40,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.95,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,感觉 和我想象中不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.40,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,它现在看起来就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.64,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,可能比我想象中厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.75,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,也可能比我想象中无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.11,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,但这之后 可能会更加繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.11,0:06:56.84,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,更加？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.74,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:07:01.68,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,要说为什么的话 因为池袋有叶香大人您在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.09,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,和我没关系吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.56,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我听说和您有关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:12.45,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,现在的池袋和叶香大人您很有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:13.43,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,说的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:16.43,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,果然比起冷清 还是繁荣更好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:17.40,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:21.10,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,既然如此 那就更高 更大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.77,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,天空也更近 更美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.26,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,果然 城里就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.38,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,来到热闹的地方 我的情绪也会高涨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:34.84,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,安静的时候您会心情低落吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.00,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,安静的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.63,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,安静且发生了什么的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.22,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,与其说是低落…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.96,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,虽然安静也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:47.98,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 不 那个 到底是怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.87,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,总之 都市也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.13,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,是的 是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:08:00.27,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,前几天 我的部下探索了涩谷 新宿 上野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.94,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,什么也没有发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.58,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这样啊 真辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.18,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,但是 池袋有公主您的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:08.75,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,所以绝好调 万事顺遂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.65,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,暗物质
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:10.17,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:12.36,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,这个 他们还没找到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:13.20,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:13.84,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,波奇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:17.59,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,现在姑且算发现了的是中微子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.26,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,那不是暗物质吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.76,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,找到的是谁来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:23.20,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,啊 是那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.20,0:08:24.67,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,喜欢电子游戏的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:25.44,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:26.91,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,电子游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.16,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,游戏先不提…公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.16,0:08:34.13,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,池袋有敌对的潜入者！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.12,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,敌对？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:36.43,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:39.94,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,他们是觉得世界很奇怪很不对 心怀不轨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:42.74,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,出现了啊！该死的魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.83,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,把消失的世界还回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.07,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,「还回来」是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:47.53,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我不是很懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:49.83,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,不管是什么全都抹消了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:52.22,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,由我？抹消了？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:52.82,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,{\an8}别装傻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.71,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,都怪你和你引发的7G事件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.46,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,世界乱七八糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.05,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,你不喜欢这个世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.84,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,这不是喜欢还是讨厌的问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.81,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,但你觉得乱七八糟了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.41,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,何等的不敬！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.41,0:09:09.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,竟敢忤逆公主的意志！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.54,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,{\an8}闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.68,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,为什么其他的线路就要被牺牲啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.23,0:09:15.34,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.29,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,什么都没被牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.29,0:09:18.74,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,以前一直都是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.56,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,而且之后也会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.63,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,这样有什么好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:24.43,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,把之前的世界还回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.82,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\pos(1064,1050)}那样的世界 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.25,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,{\pos(1592,1050)}对！没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:28.47,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,{\pos(1528,1050)}怎么可能会存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:31.24,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,{\pos(456,1050)}我知道你的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:32.64,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,{\pos(429.333,1050)}池袋的魔女！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.50,Default,Grudge Holder,0,0,0,,{\pos(445.333,1050)}你创造的池袋是赝品！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:36.62,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,{\pos(1114.667,1050)}骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.68,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.87,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,他们只是在胡思乱想！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:42.32,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,旧世界什么的根本没存在过!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.32,0:09:45.79,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,就算有 竟敢怪罪到公主的头上！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:47.64,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,哦！哦 这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:49.81,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,阴谋的味道扑面而来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,罪该万死！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.26,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,知道厉害了吧你这茶碗蒸混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.01,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,忤逆公主就是这个下场！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.88,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,像这样 还热着就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:04.59,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:05.74,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,真烫啊你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.94,0:10:07.71,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊啊 又吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.22,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:10.46,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,这里风大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:15.72,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么那个人会讨厌现在的世界呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.80,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.83,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,不该很开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:22.20,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,叶香大人开心的话 我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.70,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,真的…开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:27.45,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,开心…到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:29.72,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,波奇 有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.83,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我不擅长对付那个叫门太郎什么的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.83,0:10:35.56,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,请容我暂且离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.24,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,别忘了是谁帮了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.33,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你这个无名的木头人蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:45.04,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,没我的话 你就是丧家之犬中的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:46.81,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,你就想说这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:48.45,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,记住自己的使命！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:51.17,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她最近莫名其妙的情绪不稳定！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:55.23,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果注意到任何异常 立刻报告给本人我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.34,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.31,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你真的知道吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:11:00.09,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果你敢背叛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:02.17,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,可就不只是变成茶碗蒸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,感觉一点也不像池袋线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.55,0:11:12.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,事到如今你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:16.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,爸妈看到这样的景色的话 肯定会大吃一惊的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.03,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.03,0:11:19.64,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他们多半只会「哦」一声吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:25.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实你家里 爸爸是裸鼹鼠 妈妈是树袋鼠吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对 爷爷是三叶虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:28.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我忘记还图书馆的书了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.28,0:11:31.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,逾期了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,反正肯定又是怪书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.98,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没人会借的 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.42,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实 怎么能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,和有没有人借没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不妙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,看吧 静留也同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我好像把吃剩一半的便当盒放着不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.63,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:48.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,多半放在被子上了 或者里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\pos(653.333,85)}呜哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.88,0:11:50.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,「里面」是什么意思？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,如果 继续放着的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:54.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你妈肯定会有办法的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,小熊猫吃东西之前会洗手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:11:59.60,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那是浣熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:01.69,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,所以小熊猫不会洗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.93,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她做完饭还是会好好洗餐具的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那就没事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.06,0:12:07.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你怎么这么optimism？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你是说乐观主义？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.80,0:12:11.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶你不也说总会有办法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,虽然我是这么说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,总有人会想办法处理…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,谢谢你们陪我走这一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:19.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,怎么突然说这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:22.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就 不由自主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我们不只是陪你来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是因为我们也想去才一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:28.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,嗯 而且还挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,等我们回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:32.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我得在二十一岁零三个月之前写完这躺旅程的游记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 我要看！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.22,0:12:35.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对了 那我也会出场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:37.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,确实不得不让你出场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你可要把我写得帅气一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.84,0:12:41.11,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,强大 美丽而又聪明的玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:41.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.24,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我必须如实记述
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.32,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「如实」是什么意思啦！这不都是事实嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:48.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不过 我们也不确定是否能平安回吾野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.43,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你是说我们可能会留在池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不太可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.74,0:12:53.72,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:56.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嗯 也不能说完全没有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:57.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.57,0:12:59.76,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,和叶香一起回去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:00.83,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家都在等着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.05,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:03.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,他们真的在等着我们吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:03.80,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:16.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是仙人！坐在天鹅船上的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是那个给了我们地图的大叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.51,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那个可疑的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们看那状况！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.30,0:13:21.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,是不是不太妙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.33,0:13:22.05,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不管他直接离开？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不不不不不！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,有什么可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:31.33,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,大家让一让！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:31.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:33.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实 拿绳子过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.41,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？我知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.66,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.22,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 你去把列车停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.67,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,唉 我差点以为自己要死在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.59,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不是要逆着池袋线走吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.87,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么会从池袋的方向过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.40,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不 我本应跨过吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.70,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,朝着西吾野的方向一路向西才对！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.54,0:14:11.52,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但你是从池袋的方向来的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.52,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,会不会是绕了个圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.27,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.93,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,说不定有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.01,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,让我看看地图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.27,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我先前交给你们的地图
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,在哪来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:26.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.49,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们也太不珍惜它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:30.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,可是这张地图画得也太含糊不清了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:31.62,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,有点抽象了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.69,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这张地图可是世上唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:36.01,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,揭示了这个世界现状的事物！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.18,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是睿智的结晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.86,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.56,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我们第一次相遇的地点是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.90,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,然后现在在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:45.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:48.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这莫非是东吾野的蘑菇？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:48.76,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那这就是武藏横手的山羊人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:53.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这些是稻荷山的小人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,该不会 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.70,0:14:56.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「练爱」的浑沌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也就是说这地图都对上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:14:59.70,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,所以我不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.94,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这是睿智的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:06.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}谁知道悠闲地坐在天鹅船上旅行的人会如此博闻多识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:12.17,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那你想想 人类何以知晓一百三十四亿光年外的银河？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呃 是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.48,0:15:15.64,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,是因为探索精神呀！探索精神！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.75,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,以及冷静的洞察力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:22.55,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我受探索精神的驱使 沿着高丽川溯流而上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 你提到过这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:27.60,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,然后今天 不知为何我们得以在此处再会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:29.41,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这个现象实在耐人寻味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.41,0:15:31.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是在不知不觉间调头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:34.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,有可能哦 人有时会忘记自己做过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.06,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,尤其是年纪大了以后大脑也会老化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:36.87,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.18,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我的大脑没有丝毫问题！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.88,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果要说什么有问题 那也该是这个世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.77,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们在想为什么我事到如今还要说这个是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.77,0:15:49.14,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,蘑菇 假巨人 僵尸 以及变为大河的高丽川！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.63,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界确实发生了天翻地覆的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.63,0:15:54.87,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但我想说的是 当下仍在继续的变化！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:57.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,仍在继续的变化是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:59.97,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世界正在收缩 而池袋则在膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:02.50,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这个世界的法则变得越发混乱不堪！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.50,0:16:04.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别说这么难懂的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.23,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你说膨胀 是想说繁荣口误了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.85,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不对！就是膨胀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.85,0:16:11.26,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋正扭曲地不断膨胀着！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你说得真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:15.05,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,膨胀之后会变成什么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:15.93,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是在说池袋？那吾野呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.80,0:16:20.21,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,全部都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没办法阻止吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:22.11,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:22.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这么斩钉截铁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:23.90,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这就是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.19,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.33,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,城里不是有很多大人物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.33,0:16:29.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么他们啥也没做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:31.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那些大人物 真的还在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我从来没想过这些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.96,0:16:35.17,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那可不行 必须好好思考呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:35.98,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.88,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果他们打算采取任何行动 那早就尽其所能了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.06,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,终究只能靠我们自己想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:44.23,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:44.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:49.34,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,存在于池袋的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.14,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,拒绝让这个混乱世界变好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.34,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果你们去往池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:58.13,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,也许会直面那股可怕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.13,0:16:59.86,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们有这个觉悟吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:01.37,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.47,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,别乱动 好好待着！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.09,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,我的帽子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.60,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,手背皲裂的邮局回响
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:12.49,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,咨询少量的眼药水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:15.09,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,果然不是平时那顶帽子不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:18.84,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,毒太郎的喵喵手术就此无法恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:20.00,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.89,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,7G 暴走 不能停止的话 就连池袋都会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.89,0:17:29.53,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,必须找到7G的根源 修复这个坏掉的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:34.85,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,然后粉碎毒太郎进一步的企图 阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:36.12,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,有点好转了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:37.15,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:39.08,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,池袋会消失是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.91,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,熵的增长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.47,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,宇宙膨胀的微缩版
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:44.48,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,大撕裂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.20,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,肥皂泡消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.90,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,破裂 消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.79,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,别讲理论了 到底什么时候会消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.90,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,帽帽 帽帽帽 帽母帽帽帽 帽帽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.11,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,不知道？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:18:00.10,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,可能是明天 也可能是二十年后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.72,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,谁都无法预知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:05.04,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,善治郎 你说了有损工程师身份的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.99,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.99,0:18:09.23,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,冷静冷静冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.91,0:18:13.48,Default,Makoto,0,0,0,,若是膨胀和消失无法避免的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你已经没必要再去冒险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对啊很危险的 仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.28,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,别说蠢话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:22.48,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,无论现在未来 这个世界都在持续变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.29,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,怎么可能不去见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.38,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有点荒谬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.95,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人生永远都是荒谬的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:31.22,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,仙人在7G事件以前也过着荒谬的生活吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:32.90,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,没错 简单来说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:34.65,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,七顛八倒 乱七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.65,0:18:36.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你是为了什么才去池袋？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:39.88,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不去问这种事的才是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.32,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,睿智的结晶 修订版
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:43.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,新的地图？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.32,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.09,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果你们要去池袋的话应该能起到作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那 这是地图的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,带上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:54.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们接下来还有不少食物 但仙人就不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:58.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,接下来你要去的地方说不定会很冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:01.35,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那这些东西我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:04.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,虽说如此 我们可能明天又会突然相遇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.69,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那也有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.23,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,世上没有一件事是注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.70,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,多加小心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:11.55,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:11.96,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:16.33,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果认为膨胀后的池袋安全又繁荣的话就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:17.35,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,完全相反才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.85,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,那里的居民无法出来 于是将那里封闭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.88,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,我只是侥幸才能站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.76,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女王就是深渊本身！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,深渊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:32.47,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,她是由谜团 未知和恐惧组成的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:35.31,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女王 是叶香吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.31,0:19:38.83,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,可能是那个名字 但是我忘了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,叶香可不会做坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:43.46,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,人会变 世界也会变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.72,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,难道有一成不变之物吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:47.70,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:49.19,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:52.13,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,但那只是看起来一样而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:57.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所谓一成不变 是为了停留在某处而不断运动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.35,0:19:58.33,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.33,0:20:00.72,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,永恒和不灭是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,为什么最后非得说点儿讨厌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:04.38,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,不 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.38,0:20:04.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.14,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们已经听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:09.03,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,想要见识变化的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.47,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,和想要夺回不灭的你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.16,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就是这样才有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:18.24,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,如果我能找到你们故乡吾野再往后的西吾野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:23.16,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,或者突然发现了西武新宿线或者东武东上线的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.95,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,到那时我就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.48,Default,Swan Hermit,0,0,0,,就这样 珍重！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:28.05,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,很帅气地离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:30.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,具体来说要怎样才会回来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.29,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎样呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.11,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,草饼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:40.69,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这么说这个呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.36,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.36,0:20:42.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,但是这是个大碗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:44.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,到处都调查过了倒是能看懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:46.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,但是绘画水平很微妙啊仙人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.20,0:20:47.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,想吃草饼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,豆沙馅！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:49.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,啊？是澄沙馅吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:50.42,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真是不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,懂行的都吃豆沙馅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,叶香 还安好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:57.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,肯定很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.10,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,稍微感觉有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:03.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,照片里的叶香 和过去完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:06.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,池袋的魔女 到底是什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:10.58,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那一定是搞错了或误解了什么 我坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:13.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那可是叶香啊 她那么文静
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.89,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不可能是魔女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:18.87,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,也许 叶香被某些坏人裹挟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:30.71,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:32.97,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,大泉学园传来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:36.30,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,有一些往池袋来的麻烦的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:38.27,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,她们好像还认识公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:42.29,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,如果是过去的朋友 让她恢复记忆了就出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:46.32,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,我姑且告知了椎名町实行戒严 但我们得做两手准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.32,0:21:48.07,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,做好清除她们的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.22,Default,Pontaro,0,0,0,,你的职责是保护好公主
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.42,Default,Pochi,0,0,0,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:05.79,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,我这是在做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:09.76,Yoka,Yoka,0,0,0,,为什么我会处在这样的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:05.90,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,本视频由S1百综字幕组汉化\N仅供学习交流,严禁用于商业用途,请于24小时内删除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:23.00,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,叶香的房间和吾野的一样\N家具摆放也相同\N这是无意识的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.79,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,学校也和吾野的一样\N当然 这也是无意识的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.48,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,吾野成为苦瓜产地是在7G事件之后\N所以叶香并不知道这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:19.42,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,7G事件的始作俑者毒太郎\N并没有预料到这种情况\N很久以前就有人指出危险性\N但却一直被认为是负面宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:24.67,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这位是小柴昌俊\N已逝的日本物理学家\N喜欢的游戏是\N最终幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.68,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,这人来自东武东上线的上板桥站\N7G事件前恰好来到了池袋\N7G之后一直没能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.95,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,变成茶碗蒸的人消失了\N但是消失与死不同\N和上集的小苏是一样的\N本作中真死了的是\N东吾野的蘑菇人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:39.24,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,虽然把照顾叶香的工作推给了波奇\N但是二人接近时毒太郎会感到烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:45.04,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,波奇拥有人类的身体\N来自西武池袋线沿线的某个车站
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:44.80,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,右边是练马高野台\N左边是富士见台\N和上集隔了石神井公园
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:17.96,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,背景音是练马高野台的青蛙\N它们是气魄十足的勇士\N经常被「池袋新闻」报导\N毒太郎认为它们是\N可憎的叛乱分子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:34.65,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,天鹅仙人在 7G 之前\N没有梦想也没有希望\N过着懒散的生活\N7G 事件对天鹅仙人\N产生了非常积极的影响\N激发了他的求知欲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:54.32,annotation,annotation,0,0,0,,与上次见面相比\N天鹅仙人稍微聪明了点\N静留她们稍微温柔了点\N这不是7G的影响 而是旅行的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.36,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.75,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Shoo shoo train 終 終 トレイン
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.60,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.50,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,しょっちゅう 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.96,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,仲良くゆこう 電車乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.23,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,大好きなもの リュックに詰めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:57.96,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ほらここが始発駅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:05.50,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ラララ 知らない場所へ導いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:11.46,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,キミを探す旅へ出るのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.42,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.20,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワクワクスル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.73,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.30,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,響け ホイッスル
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:27.40,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,世界が脱線しちゃっても大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:32.26,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,ワタシたちは進んでく どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:40.83,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,次はどんな扉を開けようか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:46.14,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,さあ 終わんない旅へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:51.18,op - j,op_j,0,0,0,,Ga-tan go-ton ga-tan go-ton
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.36,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.36,0:01:36.75,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,咻 咻 train 终 终 列车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.75,0:01:38.60,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:41.50,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,总是 停止 停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:45.96,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们亲密地乘上电车出发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.23,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,将喜爱的东西装进背包
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:57.96,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,来吧 这里就是 始发站
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:05.50,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,啦啦啦 列车带着我们驶向未知的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:11.46,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,开启寻找你的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.42,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.20,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,心动不已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.73,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:22.30,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,鸣响吧 汽笛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.30,0:02:27.40,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,即使世界脱轨也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:32.26,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,我们会继续向前 不管去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:40.83,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,列车的门扉再次打开时 那又会是怎样的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.83,0:02:46.14,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,走吧 踏上永不完结的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:51.18,op - train,op_chs,0,0,0,,哐当 咕咚 哐当 咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:19.17,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しい人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:26.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,頼れる人のなり方を 誰か教えてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:45.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,雨に濡れて傘も差せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:49.38,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,いることもどうでもよくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:53.18,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,明るさが急に怖くなって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:57.45,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃないよ 大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:23:01.68,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,一緒に歩くの嫌になって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,でもひとりでいたいわけじゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:09.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,目を合わせて笑えなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:14.70,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,大丈夫じゃない それは大丈夫じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:19.58,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,何度 傷つけ 間違って 失敗して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:24.05,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,優しさ蔑ろにしただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:27.65,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,傷ついて 許して 許されて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.43,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,お前は生きろと言われただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.35,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,みんなひとりぼっちだけど 孤独だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:39.26,op - j,ed_jap,0,0,0,,あなただけここにいれば 孤独じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.53,0:22:19.17,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.17,0:22:26.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,多希望有人能告诉我 如何成为一个可靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.73,0:22:45.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,任由雨水打湿自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.56,0:22:49.38,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,也无所谓撑不撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:53.18,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,突然对光明感到恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:57.45,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 我很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.24,0:23:01.68,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,变得讨厌与他人并肩而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:05.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,但又并非是想要孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:09.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我们视线相交 却无法展露笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:14.70,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我很不安啊 这很不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.05,0:23:19.58,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我无数次伤害你 误会你 犯下错误
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:24.05,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,那都是因为我忽视了你的温柔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:27.65,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,我受到伤害 宽恕他人 被他人谅解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.95,0:23:31.43,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,这都是因为你曾鼓励我活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:35.35,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,虽然大家形单影只 但这绝非孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.78,0:23:39.26,ed - train,ed_chs,0,0,0,,只要你仍身处此地 这便不是孤独
